    AbstractDatabase
    Abstract base class for database API implementations.
    AbstractDatabase.Parameterizer
    Parameterization class.
    Database
    Database specifies the requirements for any database implementation.
    DatabaseEventManager
    Class to manage database events such as insertions and removals.
    DatabaseEventManager.Type
    Types for aggregation.
    HashmapDatabase
    Database storing data using hashtable storage, and thus allowing additional and removal of objects.
    StaticArrayDatabase
    This database class uses array-based storage and thus does not allow for dynamic insert, delete and update operations.
    UpdatableDatabase
    Database API with updates.
